Here are some Quick Facts on the report that involves mention of two vaccine ingredients (antigens) that may not be familiar to most people.

This video was issued on the David Icke site on June 17, 2020.

The Video is from David Knight Show of Info Wars

Note that both the man reporting in the video, Ben Fellows, and David Knight, who presents it to us, show a certain level of scepticism about the claims. Ben Fellows’ strategy will be to get access to the vaccine and the trials in order that vaccines may be lab-tested independently.

Ben Fellows comes from the group www.govote.org.uk and reports on information received from a GlaxoSmithKline whistleblower on what is believed to be some of the ingredients in the vaccine (or one of them) currently being trialled. .
